<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en" data-theme="dark">
  <head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1" />
    <title>RCM Validation Survey | BrainSAIT Research</title>
    <meta name="description" content="Revenue Cycle Management (RCM) validation survey and outreach toolkit by BrainSAIT for healthcare professionals in Saudi Arabia." />
    <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.gstatic.com" crossorigin />
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Inter:wght@400;500;600;700&display=swap" rel="stylesheet" />
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/assets/styles.css" />
    <script defer src="/config.js"></script>
    <script defer src="/assets/app.js"></script>
  </head>
  <body>
    <header class="site-header" role="banner">
      <div class="brand">
        <div class="logo" aria-label="BrainSAIT">🧠 BrainSAIT</div>
        <div class="tagline">Healthcare AI Research Initiative</div>
      </div>
      <div class="header-actions">
        <button id="langToggle" class="chip" title="Toggle direction" aria-pressed="false">LTR</button>
      </div>
    </header>

    <main class="container" role="main">
      <section class="card survey" aria-labelledby="survey-title">
        <div class="accent"></div>
        <h1 id="survey-title" class="visually-hidden">RCM Validation Survey</h1>

        <div class="progress" aria-label="Survey progress" aria-live="polite">
          <div class="progress-bar"><div class="progress-fill" id="progressBar" style="width: 0%"></div></div>
          <div class="progress-text"><span id="progressText">Step 1 of 6</span></div>
        </div>

        <form id="surveyForm" novalidate>
          <!-- Q1 - Enhanced for Saudi Healthcare Context -->
          <fieldset class="question active" data-question="1" aria-describedby="q1-help">
            <legend class="question-title">ما هو دورك في إدارة دورة الإيرادات الصحية؟ | What's your role in healthcare revenue cycle management?</legend>
            <p id="q1-help" class="question-subtitle">نحن نبحث في تحديات إدارة الإيرادات لتطوير حلول أفضل للقطاع الصحي السعودي | We're researching RCM challenges to develop better solutions for Saudi healthcare.</p>
            <div class="options-grid">
              <button type="button" class="option" data-value="rcm-director" data-qualify="high">
                <span class="option-title">مدير/مديرة الإيرادات | RCM Director/Manager</span>
                <span class="option-desc">مسؤول مباشر عن عمليات دورة الإيرادات | Direct responsibility for revenue cycle operations</span>
              </button>
              <button type="button" class="option" data-value="practice-admin" data-qualify="high">
                <span class="option-title">مدير/ة العيادة | Practice Administrator</span>
                <span class="option-desc">إشراف على عمليات العيادة والفوترة | Oversee clinic operations including billing</span>
              </button>
              <button type="button" class="option" data-value="billing-manager" data-qualify="high">
                <span class="option-title">مدير/ة الفوترة | Billing Manager/Supervisor</span>
                <span class="option-desc">إدارة فريق وعمليات الفوترة | Manage billing team and processes</span>
              </button>
              <button type="button" class="option" data-value="it-manager" data-qualify="medium">
                <span class="option-title">مدير/ة تقنية المعلومات | IT Manager</span>
                <span class="option-desc">إدارة الأنظمة التقنية الصحية | Managing healthcare IT systems</span>
              </button>
              <button type="button" class="option" data-value="clinical-supervisor" data-qualify="medium">
                <span class="option-title">مشرف/ة إكلينيكي | Clinical Supervisor</span>
                <span class="option-desc">إشراف على الفرق الطبية والتوثيق | Supervising medical teams and documentation</span>
              </button>
              <button type="button" class="option" data-value="quality-manager" data-qualify="medium">
                <span class="option-title">مدير/ة الجودة | Quality Manager</span>
                <span class="option-desc">ضمان الجودة والامتثال للمعايير | Quality assurance and compliance</span>
              </button>
              <button type="button" class="option" data-value="finance-controller" data-qualify="high">
                <span class="option-title">مراقب/ة مالي | Finance Controller</span>
                <span class="option-desc">مراقبة الأداء المالي والتدفق النقدي | Financial performance and cash flow monitoring</span>
              </button>
              <button type="button" class="option" data-value="other-healthcare" data-qualify="low">
                <span class="option-title">أخصائي/ة صحي آخر | Other Healthcare Professional</span>
                <span class="option-desc">مشارك في القطاع الصحي | Involved in healthcare sector</span>
              </button>
            </div>
          </fieldset>

          <!-- Q2 - Enhanced Organization Size with Saudi Context -->
          <fieldset class="question" data-question="2">
            <legend class="question-title">كم عدد مقدمي الرعاية الصحية في منظمتك؟ | How many healthcare providers does your organization have?</legend>
            <p class="question-subtitle">يساعدنا هذا في فهم حجم تحديات إدارة الإيرادات | This helps us understand the scale of your RCM challenges.</p>
            <div class="options-grid">
              <button type="button" class="option" data-value="mega-system" data-qualify="high">
                <span class="option-title">500+ مقدم خدمة | 500+ Providers</span>
                <span class="option-desc">نظام صحي كبير أو مجموعة مستشفيات | Large health system or hospital group</span>
              </button>
              <button type="button" class="option" data-value="large" data-qualify="high">
                <span class="option-title">100-500 مقدم خدمة | 100-500 Providers</span>
                <span class="option-desc">مستشفى كبير أو مجموعة تخصصات | Large hospital or multi-specialty group</span>
              </button>
              <button type="button" class="option" data-value="medium" data-qualify="high">
                <span class="option-title">20-100 مقدم خدمة | 20-100 Providers</span>
                <span class="option-desc">مستشفى متوسط أو عيادة كبيرة | Mid-size hospital or large clinic</span>
              </button>
              <button type="button" class="option" data-value="small" data-qualify="medium">
                <span class="option-title">5-20 مقدم خدمة | 5-20 Providers</span>
                <span class="option-desc">عيادة صغيرة إلى متوسطة | Small to medium practice</span>
              </button>
              <button type="button" class="option" data-value="very-small" data-qualify="low">
                <span class="option-title">أقل من 5 مقدمين | Less than 5 Providers</span>
                <span class="option-desc">عيادة صغيرة أو طبيب منفرد | Small clinic or solo practitioner</span>
              </button>
            </div>
          </fieldset>

          <!-- Q3 - Enhanced Challenges for Saudi Healthcare -->
          <fieldset class="question" data-question="3">
            <legend class="question-title">ما هو أكبر تحدٍ في إدارة الإيرادات حالياً؟ | What's your biggest RCM challenge right now?</legend>
            <p class="question-subtitle">اختر التحدي الذي يؤثر أكثر على منظمتك | Select the challenge that impacts your organization most.</p>
            <div class="options-grid">
              <button type="button" class="option" data-value="nphies-compliance" data-qualify="high">
                <span class="option-title">امتثال نفيس والتأمين | NPHIES Compliance & Insurance</span>
                <span class="option-desc">صعوبات في الامتثال لنظام نفيس ومطالبات التأمين | Challenges with NPHIES compliance and insurance claims</span>
              </button>
              <button type="button" class="option" data-value="staffing-shortage" data-qualify="high">
                <span class="option-title">نقص الكوادر المتخصصة | Skilled Staff Shortage</span>
                <span class="option-desc">صعوبة إيجاد والاحتفاظ بموظفين مؤهلين | Can't find or retain qualified RCM staff</span>
              </button>
              <button type="button" class="option" data-value="manual-processes" data-qualify="high">
                <span class="option-title">العمليات اليدوية | Manual Processes</span>
                <span class="option-desc">كثرة الإدخال اليدوي والمتابعات | Too much manual data entry and follow-up</span>
              </button>
              <button type="button" class="option" data-value="denial-management" data-qualify="high">
                <span class="option-title">إدارة الرفض والمراجعات | Denial Management</span>
                <span class="option-desc">ارتفاع معدلات رفض المطالبات | High denial rates and claim rejections</span>
              </button>
              <button type="button" class="option" data-value="system-integration" data-qualify="medium">
                <span class="option-title">تكامل الأنظمة | System Integration</span>
                <span class="option-desc">صعوبة ربط الأنظمة المختلفة | Difficulty integrating different systems</span>
              </button>
              <button type="button" class="option" data-value="cash-flow" data-qualify="medium">
                <span class="option-title">التدفق النقدي | Cash Flow Issues</span>
                <span class="option-desc">بطء التحصيل وتأخير المدفوعات | Slow collections and payment delays</span>
              </button>
            </div>
          </fieldset>

          <!-- Q4: Enhanced SAR ranges with more realistic Saudi healthcare figures -->
          <fieldset class="question" data-question="4">
            <legend class="question-title">الخسائر الشهرية المقدرة بسبب عدم كفاءة إدارة الإيرادات (ريال سعودي) | Estimated monthly revenue lost due to RCM inefficiencies (SAR)</legend>
            <p class="question-subtitle">تشمل المطالبات المرفوضة وتأخير المدفوعات وتكاليف الموظفين | Include denied claims, delayed payments, and staffing costs.</p>
            <div class="options-grid">
              <button type="button" class="option" data-value="critical-impact" data-qualify="high" data-sar="1000000">
                <span class="option-title">مليون ريال سعودي أو أكثر | SAR 1,000,000+</span>
                <span class="option-desc">تأثير مالي حرج يتطلب تدخل فوري | Critical financial impact requiring immediate intervention</span>
              </button>
              <button type="button" class="option" data-value="high-impact" data-qualify="high" data-sar="500000">
                <span class="option-title">500,000 - 1,000,000 ريال | SAR 500,000 - 1,000,000</span>
                <span class="option-desc">تأثير مالي كبير ومقلق | Significant and concerning financial impact</span>
              </button>
              <button type="button" class="option" data-value="medium-impact" data-qualify="high" data-sar="250000">
                <span class="option-title">250,000 - 500,000 ريال | SAR 250,000 - 500,000</span>
                <span class="option-desc">تأثير متوسط ولكن ملحوظ | Moderate but noticeable impact</span>
              </button>
              <button type="button" class="option" data-value="low-impact" data-qualify="medium" data-sar="100000">
                <span class="option-title">100,000 - 250,000 ريال | SAR 100,000 - 250,000</span>
                <span class="option-desc">تأثير ملحوظ يستدعي التحسين | Noticeable impact requiring improvement</span>
              </button>
              <button type="button" class="option" data-value="minimal" data-qualify="low" data-sar="50000">
                <span class="option-title">أقل من 100,000 ريال | Less than SAR 100,000</span>
                <span class="option-desc">تأثير محدود ولكن قابل للتحسين | Limited impact but room for improvement</span>
              </button>
            </div>
          </fieldset>

          <!-- Q5 - Enhanced AI/Technology Adoption with Saudi Context -->
          <fieldset class="question" data-question="5">
            <legend class="question-title">مدى استعداد منظمتك لتبني الذكاء الاصطناعي في إدارة الإيرادات؟ | How ready is your organization to adopt AI automation for RCM?</legend>
            <p class="question-subtitle">يساعدنا هذا في فهم مستوى الاستعداد للحلول الجديدة | This helps us understand readiness for new solutions.</p>
            <div class="options-grid">
              <button type="button" class="option" data-value="ai-pioneer" data-qualify="high">
                <span class="option-title">رائد في التقنية | Technology Pioneer</span>
                <span class="option-desc">نطبق حلول الذكاء الاصطناعي بنشاط | Actively implementing AI solutions</span>
              </button>
              <button type="button" class="option" data-value="very-open" data-qualify="high">
                <span class="option-title">منفتح جداً | Very Open</span>
                <span class="option-desc">نسعى بنشاط لحلول الذكاء الاصطناعي | Actively seeking AI/automation solutions</span>
              </button>
              <button type="button" class="option" data-value="open-with-pilot" data-qualify="high">
                <span class="option-title">منفتح مع التجريب | Open with Piloting</span>
                <span class="option-desc">نفضل تجربة الحلول قبل التطبيق الكامل | Prefer to pilot solutions before full implementation</span>
              </button>
              <button type="button" class="option" data-value="cautious-proven" data-qualify="medium">
                <span class="option-title">حذر ولكن مهتم | Cautious but Interested</span>
                <span class="option-desc">نحتاج لأدلة قوية وحالات نجاح محلية | Need strong evidence and local success cases</span>
              </button>
              <button type="button" class="option" data-value="traditional-focus" data-qualify="low">
                <span class="option-title">تركيز تقليدي | Traditional Focus</span>
                <span class="option-desc">نفضل الطرق التقليدية المثبتة | Prefer proven traditional approaches</span>
              </button>
              <button type="button" class="option" data-value="regulatory-concerns" data-qualify="medium">
                <span class="option-title">قلق تنظيمي | Regulatory Concerns</span>
                <span class="option-desc">مهتمون ولكن قلقون من الامتثال التنظيمي | Interested but concerned about regulatory compliance</span>
              </button>
            </div>
          </fieldset>

          <!-- Q6 Contact - Enhanced with bilingual fields -->
          <fieldset class="question" data-question="6">
            <legend class="question-title">لنتواصل لمناقشة تحديات إدارة الإيرادات | Let's connect to discuss your RCM challenges</legend>
            <p class="question-subtitle">نود التعرف أكثر على وضعكم المحدد ومشاركة الرؤى ذات الصلة | We'd love to learn more about your specific situation and share relevant insights.</p>
            <div class="form-grid">
              <label class="field">
                <span>الاسم الكامل * | Full Name *</span>
                <input id="fullName" name="fullName" class="input" type="text" autocomplete="name" placeholder="مثال: د. أحمد محمد | Dr. Ahmed Mohammed" required />
              </label>
              <label class="field">
                <span>البريد الإلكتروني للعمل * | Work Email *</span>
                <input id="email" name="email" class="input" type="email" autocomplete="email" placeholder="ahmed@hospital.com.sa" required />
              </label>
              <label class="field">
                <span>المنظمة/المستشفى * | Organization/Hospital *</span>
                <input id="organization" name="organization" class="input" type="text" placeholder="مستشفى الملك فيصل التخصصي | King Faisal Specialist Hospital" required />
              </label>
              <label class="field">
                <span>رقم الهاتف (السعودية) | Phone (KSA)</span>
                <input id="phone" name="phone" class="input" type="tel" inputmode="tel" placeholder="05XXXXXXXX or +9665XXXXXXX" />
              </label>
              <label class="field">
                <span>المدينة، المنطقة | Location (City, Region)</span>
                <input id="location" name="location" class="input" type="text" placeholder="الرياض، المنطقة الوسطى | Riyadh, Central Region" />
              </label>
              <label class="field">
                <span>المسمى الوظيفي | Job Title</span>
                <input id="jobTitle" name="jobTitle" class="input" type="text" placeholder="مدير الإيرادات | Revenue Manager" />
              </label>
            </div>
          </fieldset>

          <div class="nav">
            <button type="button" class="btn secondary" id="prevBtn" disabled>← Previous</button>
            <button type="button" class="btn primary" id="nextBtn" disabled>Next →</button>
          </div>
        </form>

        <section class="results" id="resultsSection" hidden>
          <div id="qualificationBadge" class="badge">Thank you</div>
          <p id="qualificationText" class="muted"></p>
          <div class="cta">
            <a id="bookLink" href="#" class="btn primary" target="_blank" rel="noopener">📅 Book a 15‑Minute Chat</a>
            <button id="submitBtn" class="btn secondary">📧 Send My Responses</button>
          </div>
          <p id="submitNote" class="muted small"></p>
        </section>
      </section>

      <section class="card outreach" aria-labelledby="outreach-title">
        <div class="accent"></div>
        <h2 id="outreach-title">📧 Outreach Scripts</h2>

        <article class="script">
          <h3>LinkedIn Message</h3>
          <pre id="linkedin-script" class="script-box">Hi [Name],

I saw your profile and noticed you work in healthcare revenue cycle management at [Company] in KSA.

I’m conducting research on RCM challenges in Saudi Arabia (staffing shortages, denial rates, manual processes) and would love your perspective.

Would you be open to a quick 2-minute survey that could help the industry find better solutions?

[Survey Link]

No sales pitch – just research to understand real challenges. Happy to share insights from the study with you.

Best regards,
Dr. Mohamed El Fadil Abuagla
BrainSAIT Healthcare AI Research</pre>
          <button class="chip" data-copy="linkedin-script">Copy</button>
        </article>

        <article class="script">
          <h3>Email Outreach</h3>
          <pre id="email-script" class="script-box">Subject: Quick RCM Research – Your Expert Perspective (KSA)

Hi [Name],

I hope you’re well. I’m Dr. Mohamed El Fadil Abuagla, researching revenue cycle management challenges in KSA healthcare organizations.

Given your role as [Title] at [Company], I’d value your insights—especially around staffing shortages, denial management, and process automation.

Could you spare 2 minutes for a brief survey? It’s anonymous; I’m happy to share aggregated findings.

[Survey Link]

This isn’t a sales outreach – I’m genuinely researching to understand industry challenges and potential solutions for the Saudi market.

If you’re open, I’d also be happy to schedule a short call at your convenience.

Best regards,
Dr. Mohamed El Fadil Abuagla
Founder, BrainSAIT – Healthcare AI Research Initiative
dr.mf.12298@gmail.com</pre>
          <button class="chip" data-copy="email-script">Copy</button>
        </article>

        <article class="script">
          <h3>Follow‑up Email</h3>
          <pre id="followup-script" class="script-box">Subject: Re: RCM Research – Thank you

Hi [Name],

Thank you for completing the RCM survey. Your insights about [specific challenge] are very helpful.

Based on your responses, you might find our upcoming findings relevant—especially regarding [specific area].

Would you be open to a brief 15‑minute conversation? I can share preliminary insights that may be useful for your organization in KSA.

[Calendly Link]

Warm regards,
Dr. Mohamed El Fadil Abuagla
BrainSAIT Healthcare AI Research</pre>
          <button class="chip" data-copy="followup-script">Copy</button>
        </article>
      </section>
    </main>

    <footer class="site-footer" role="contentinfo">
      <div>© <span id="year"></span> BrainSAIT Research • Saudi Arabia</div>
    </footer>
  </body>
</html>
